«WHO SHOULD A graduate of the majoring in Mechanical Engineering Technology can:

▶ ️ Mechanical engineer on an industrial line or in a workshop in a metal construction company, ship repair yards, various mechanical industries, quarries and mines. Can manage a department, production process, deal with LEAN methods in a company, be a welding technologist;
▶ ️ an engineer-designer who works in a technology company, in companies dealing with robots, in a company that manufactures machines (lifting and conveying machines, robots, measuring devices, etc.);
▶ ️ a quality manager who works in welding companies and companies where it is necessary to weld different constructions (this person evaluates the quality of the weld and gives instructions on welding technology), as well as is engaged in optimal production, ie smart production;
▶ ️ A equipment calibrator who works in laboratories and calibrates a variety of equipment, both electrical and mechanical and optical, can become an assessor with greater experience, assessing other laboratories and assessing accreditation.

👉 Don't wait! Apply today!
