The Oil Shale Competence Center of TalTech Virumaa College, which operates at the College, has been publishing an oil shale newsletter since 2015. 👉 The latest news is already here!

TalTech Virumaa College Oil Shale Competence Center
27 April 2020 at 14:55 ·

📢 In the new oil shale newsletter you can read:

- how are Eesti Energia and Viru Keemia Grupp doing the Estonian oil shale industries;
- Mare Roosileht, Director of TalTech Virumaa College, will discuss how a successful oil shale revolution could take place;
- Professor Allan Niidu's opinion on future fuels;
- the Ministry of the Environment writes about the plans to amend the Crustal Act, the cleaning of the Purtse River catchment area and the plans for the elimination of landslides;
- safer technological solutions in mining;
- the results of the analysis of the possibilities for a fair transition by the think tank Praxis

and more.

